usage: scl enable|run [<collection>...] <command>
       scl load|unload [<collection>...]
       scl list-collections
       scl list-packages|man|register|deregister <collection>
       scl --help

description:
    enable|run            run given command from Software Collection 
    load|unload           enable/disable collection in current shell
    list-collections      list installed Software Collections
    list-packages         list pacages in Sofware Collection
    man                   show manual paga about Software Collection
    register|deregister   register/deregister Sofware Collection
    --help                show this help

Use '-' as <command> to read the command from standard input.
